Class CurveId

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.opengamma.strata.market.curve.CurveId
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MarketDataId<Curve>, NamedMarketDataId<Curve>, java.io.Serializable, Bean, ImmutableBean
    public final class CurveId
extends java.lang.Object
implements NamedMarketDataId<Curve>, ImmutableBean, java.io.Serializable
    An identifier used to access a curve by name.

    This is used when there is a need to obtain an instance of Curve.
